<paragraph blockId="20.[151,814,1406,1466]" box="[151,235,1441,1466]" pageId="20" pageNumber="421">
(
<figureCitation box="[159,227,1441,1466]" captionStart="FIGURE 9" captionStartId="21.[151,250,1887,1909]" captionTargetBox="[340,1247,695,1869]" captionTargetId="figure@21.[340,1247,695,1869]" captionTargetPageId="21" captionText="FIGURE 9. Wroughtonia areolata sp. nov. ♀, holotype. A, wings; B, mesosoma, lateral aspect; C, first-third metasomal tergites, dorsal aspect; D, hind femur and tibia, lateral aspect; E, propodeum, medio-dorsal aspect; F, habitus, lateral aspect; G, head, lateral aspect; H, head, dorsal aspect; I, apex of ovipositor sheath, lateral aspect. J, detail of frontal protuberance, laterodorsal aspect." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/827544/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="421">Fig. 9</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
